=== Prince of Cannock Equipment ===
Can use most equipment but limited to lighter weapons:
* Swords
* Boomerangs
* Staffs
* Light armor

=== Princess of Moonbrooke Equipment ===
Limited to:
* Staffs and wands
* Robes and light armor
* Magic-focused items

