== Cursed Equipment ==

Some equipment is cursed:
* Sword of Destruction - High attack but cursed
* Mad Cap - Defense but cursed
* Cursed items cannot be unequipped without church

== Erdrick's Equipment ==

=== Dragon Quest I ===
The legendary equipment set:
* Erdrick's Sword - Charlock Castle
* Erdrick's Armor - Hauksness (search ruins)

=== Dragon Quest II ===
* Erdrick's Sword - Cave of Rendarak
* Erdrick's Shield - Wellgarth area
* Erdrick's Helm - Tower of the Moon
* Erdrick's Armor - Hargon's Castle

== Shop Locations ==

=== DQ1 Major Shops ===
* Brecconary - Basic equipment
* Garinham - Medium equipment
* Rimuldar - Magic Armor, advanced items
* Cantlin - High-end equipment

=== DQ2 Major Shops ===
* Leftwyne - Starting area
* Moonbrooke region - Mid-game
* Rhone merchants - End-game

== Equipment Tips ==

'''Dragon Quest I:'''
* Magic Armor heals HP while walking - very useful
* Save for Erdrick's equipment over buying expensive alternatives

'''Dragon Quest II:'''
* Falcon Sword's double attack can be better than higher attack weapons
* Princess has limited options - focus on magic items
* Shield of Strength provides sustainability

